Selected Valuation Methodology.

IEnova Pipelines is a regulated business, that will earn a return of its costs and a reasonable return on its invested capital, without other consideration; the value of the assets of a regulated business is the value of its invested capital, Under this premise, the FV of the ﬁxed assets ofregulated businesses is equivalent to carrying value for ﬁnancial reporting purposes, as carrying value reﬂects the basis for which invested capital is derived, and for which a regulated business is allowed to earn a reasonable

return.

The Company concluded that the cairying value of the ﬁxed assets is deemed to be representative of FV for IFRS purposes.
